description: BMO Low Volatility Emerging Markets Equity ETF has been designed to provide exposure to a low beta weighted portfolio of emerging markets stocks. Beta measures the security's sensitivity to market movements. The ETF utilizes a rules based methodology to build a portfolio of less market sensitive stocks from a universe of emerging market large cap stocks. The underlying portfolio is rebalanced in May and reconstituted in November.
name: BMO Low Volatility International Equity Hedged to CAD ETF
